title: 141: The Costco Haul Episode (April '21 Edition)
itunes:title: The Costco Haul Episode (April '21 Edition)
description: In this episode, Lisa and the gang are trying some great food finds from Costco! Finds like sous vide beef sirloin, beef tri-tip, ratatouille, uniquely different salsa, watermelon jerky, and SO MUCH MORE! Plus, the find of all finds… a salmon dip with everything bagel seasoning in it! It’s INCREDIBLE!!! Wait no more — push play now, and then head on over to our Foodcast page for a list of the finds mentioned in the episode!
itunes:summary: Time to head down to Costco and check out their new spring food finds on this week’s episode of Chew the Right Thing!
itunes:author: Lisa Lillien
